tiers.ability_description: Light Side allies have +100% Critical Chance while attacking out of turn.
At the start of each Rogue One ally's turn, if they have not taken damage since their last turn, they gain Critical Chance Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Jyn Erso critically hits an enemy, Jyn Erso gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.
Whenever Light Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.
Whenever a Unaligned Force User ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the target enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Ahsoka Tano (Fulcrum) gains Retribution, they also gain 10% Defense and 10% Health Steal (stacking, max 200%), and 10 Speed (stacking, max 200) until the end of encounter.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Pirate allies inflict a debuff on an enemy during their turn, they deal bonus damage equal to 10% of that enemy's Max Health, which can't be evaded.
Whenever Quiggold is dealt damage, reflect 20% of the damage dealt back onto the attacker as True damage, which can't be evaded. This damage can't defeat enemies.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.

If all allies are First Order at the start of battle, First Order allies gain Damage Immunity for 2 turns. Whenever a First Order ally is critically hit, all First Order allies gain 10% Critical Damage (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter. Whenever a First Order ally attacks out of turn, all First Order allies gain 10% Offense (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter.

Whenever Supreme Leader Kylo Ren has 100 or more stacks of Siphon, he ignores Stealth and Taunt during his turn. For every 20 stacks of Siphon he has, First Order allies gain 10% Defense and 10% Health Steal (stacking, max 200%) until the end of the encounter.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
Whenever a Unaligned Force User ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the target enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Ben Solo deals damage to an enemy, remove 25% Turn Meter from that enemy.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.
Whenever a First Order ally has full Health and Protection at the start of their turn, they deal +100% more Damage on their turn.
At the beginning of their turn, Light Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all debuffs on themself.
Whenever Unaligned Force User allies critically hit an enemy during their turn, that ally gains 10% Offense (stacking) for 2 turns.

Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker damages an enemy with a Special ability and the enemy doesn't have Armor Shred, inflict Armor Shred on them for the rest of the battle. Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker uses a Basic ability and damages an enemy with Armor Shred, inflict Expose for 2 turns, which can't be resisted, and Commander Luke Skywalker gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns.
At the beginning of their turn, Light Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all debuffs on themself.
The first time each Unaligned Force User ally falls below 50% Health they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn and gain Health Steal Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Cere Junda uses a Basic ability on their turn, other allies gain +25% Turn Meter.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain Tenacity Up, they gain Protection Up (10%, stacking) for 2 turns.
Whenever Light Side allies are evaded by an enemy, that ally gains Accuracy Up for 2 turns, and they inflict Evasion Down for 2 turns on that enemy, which can't be evaded.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
Dark Side allies start the battle with Protection Up (20%) for 2 turns.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.

At the start of each encounter, Dengar inflicts Doubt on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded, dispelled, or resisted.

Whenever an enemy evades Dengar's attack or resists a debuff, all enemies are inflicted with a stack of Damage Over Time and Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.
Whenever Tank allies are Stunned, gain 50% Turn Meter and recover 25% Health and Protection.

Whenever CT-5555 "Fives" attacks out of turn, CT-5555 "Fives" deals 150% bonus damage, inflicts Offense Down and Healing Immunity for 1 turn on all enemies, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever CT-5555 "Fives" loses Taunt, he removes 50% Turn Meter from all enemies and inflicts Blind on them for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.

At the start of each encounter, grant all allies Evasion Up and Tenacity Up for 2 turns and inflict Tenacity Down and Evasion Down on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a non-support ally is critically hit, grant them Protection Up (20%, stacking, max 100%) for 2 turns.

At the start of their turn, Support allies dispel all buffs on all enemies. If Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, Potency Up, or Tenacity Up were dispelled, inflict the opposite debuff on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a Support is critically hit or inflicted with a debuff, they Stealth for 1 turn.

At the start of each encounter, grant all allies Evasion Up and Tenacity Up for 2 turns and inflict Tenacity Down and Evasion Down on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a non-support ally is critically hit, grant them Protection Up (20%, stacking, max 100%) for 2 turns.

At the start of their turn, Support allies dispel all buffs on all enemies. If Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, Potency Up, or Tenacity Up were dispelled, inflict the opposite debuff on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a Support is critically hit or inflicted with a debuff, they Stealth for 1 turn.

Whenever Qui-Gon Jinn damages an enemy with a Special ability and the enemy doesn't have Armor Shred, inflict Armor Shred on them for the rest of the battle. Whenever Qui-Gon Jinn uses a Basic ability and damages an enemy with Armor Shred, inflict Expose for 2 turns, which can't be resisted, and Qui-Gon Jinn gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns.
